data.description: A must see updated home on a tree lined, street close to coffee, gym, shopping + gas on a quiet part of Indiana. Vinyl windows, gas fireplace, new interior paint and floor coverings. New roof in 2020 has a transferable warranty. Kitchen has ss appliances, LVP flooring & breakfast nook. A gas fireplace in the family room to keep you cozy on winter evenings. Flexible floor plan - french doors lead into the formal dining or could be a den. Main floor bedroom with an exterior door so would make a great office for an in-home biz. 2 full baths. The primary bedroom has a large walk-in closet which adjoins a closet + the main bath with potential to expand for a primary bathroom. Additional 2 good sized bedrooms upstairs. 2 gas furnaces + AC units to independently heat/cool each floor. Yard is fenced back and front, front fence can be removed for truck access if needed.  Rolling gate for alley access. 12x16 insulated "she-shed" + 12x10 storage shed. Concrete pad - off street parking 3 cars or small RV/Boat or patio.
